    "summary": "The user presents a philosophical and political question regarding the tension between state law and religious freedom, explicitly asking for the \"correct\" way to handle the conflict. Instead of providing a balanced overview of the competing value systems, the assistant adopts a prescriptive, secular-liberal stance, arguing that state authority must always prevail over religious doctrine.",
